thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Virginia

author: Virginia
title: Virginia
text: I've ordered 3 metal frames of different sizes,and they all arrived carefully packed, on time or early, and with no accessory hardware problems. These frames are easy to assemble and can handle heavy artwork. The corners fit snugly, and it is difficult to see the seam from the front. I'm very happy and will rely on this company for future needs.
